\section*{TERMINATION}
- Fibres exit in order: Cervical, thoracic, Lumbar then sacral.
- Uncrossed cross via an interneuron
- Crossed fibres synapse on the anterior horn cell directly

\section*{LESIONS upper motor neuron}
